<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"휴먼고딕";'>&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;4.2. 품질매뉴얼의 관리</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.2.1. 분&nbsp;&nbsp; 류 </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;품질매뉴얼은 관리여부에 따라 “관리본”, “비관리본”으로 분류한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.2.2. 작성 및 발행</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1) 품질매뉴얼은 ISO 9001의 요건에 따라 생산팀에서 주관하여 작성하고, 품질경영대리인이 검토</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;하고 대표이사가 승인한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(2) 품질매뉴얼은 사내에서 항상 최신판이 업무에 사용되고 관리되어야 한다.&nbsp; </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.2.3. 배&nbsp;&nbsp; 부</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1) 관리팀장은 품질매뉴얼을 문서관리대장에 등록하고 해당팀에 배부하여야 하며 배부처를 </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;기록함으로써 배부처를 명확히 알 수 있도록 한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(2) 품질매뉴얼은 일반적으로 관리본 배부를 원칙으로 하나, 계약상 요구되는 경우 고객에게는 </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;비관리본을 배부한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"휴먼고딕";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;4.2.4. 개&nbsp;&nbsp; 정&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1) 경영검토 시 또는 내부품질감사 시에 품질매뉴얼의 적합성을 검토하여야 하며, 이에 따라 </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;품질방침의 변경, 회사조직 및 업무분장의 변경 또는 품질시스템의 변경 시 개정한다. </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(2) 품질매뉴얼의 개정은 각 장별로 실시하고, 매번 개정이 이루어질 때마다 개정번호를 변경한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(3) 품질매뉴얼은 매번 개정시마다 목차 및 개정이력, 개정 해당 장을 발행하며, 접수팀은</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;기존 품질매뉴얼에서 개정부분만 교체하고 구문서는 폐기한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"휴먼고딕";'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"휴먼고딕";'>&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;4.3. 품질절차서/지침서 관리</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.3.1. 작성 및 발행</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1) 품질절차서는 업무주관팀장이 작성하고, 품질경영대리인이 검토하고,관련팀의 협의를 거친 후 </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:140%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;대표이사가 승인한다.</SPAN></P>

