<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"휴먼고딕";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;4.3.2. 배부 및 접수&nbsp; </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1) 관리팀장은 승인이 완료된 품질절차서 및 업무/작업지침서를 주관팀장으로부터 접수 후 문서</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;관리대장에 등록하고, 해당팀에 배부한다. 품질절차서/지침서의 접수팀은 최신본만을 유지하며&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 구본은 폐기시킨다. </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(2) 회사 내에 배부되는 품질절차서/지침서는 “관리본”만을 배부함을 원칙으로 한다. 단, 대외적으로&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 배부가 필요한 경우 “비관리본”을 배부한다. </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(3) 관리본 문서를 접수한 팀장은 파손, 분실되거나 회사 밖으로 유출되지 않도록 관리하여야 한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.3.3. 개&nbsp; 정&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1) 품질절차서/품질지침서의 변경은 특별한 사유가 없는 경우 처음 문서를 작성한 조직에 의해 검토&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 승인되어야 한다. 문서작성 조직은 그들의 책임 하에 있는 품질절차서/지침서의 적합성을 지속적&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 으로 관리하여야 한다.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(2) 품질절차서/지침서의 개정에 대한 사항은 개정이력란에 기재함으로써 개정의 근거를 명확히 한다.&nbsp; </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(3) 품질절차서/지침서는 개정 즉시 모든 관련조직에게 배부하여야 한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(4) 개정번호는 아라비아 숫자로 기입하며, 제정본인 경우 개정번호는 “0”으로 한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></P>

