<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";font-weight:"bold";'>4. 업무절차</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;4.1 품질감사계획</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.1.1 관리팀장은 매년 말 익년도 년간 품질감사계획서를 작성하여 대표이사의 승인을 득한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.1.2 연간 품질감사계획서에는 다음 사항이 포함되도록 작성한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1) 피감사팀</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(2) 감사일정</SPAN></P>

