<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";letter-spacing:0.2pt;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.2 품질감사 수행계획서의 작성</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";letter-spacing:0.2pt;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.2.1 관리팀장은 연간 품질감사계획서에 준해 최소한 품질감사 실시 10일전에</SPAN><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'> 품질감사수행계획서를&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 작성하여야 한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.2.2 관리팀장은 감사계획수립 시에 자격이 부여된 감사자를 품질감사 수행계획서의 피감사 팀에&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 배정한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.2.3 품질감사수행 계획서에는 다음 사항이 포함되도록 작성한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1) 감사구분, 감사일자/기간</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(2) 피감사 부서</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(3) 감사범위 및 내용</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.2.4 품질감사 수행계획서는 대표이사의 승인을 받아 확정되며 피감사 팀 및 감사자에게 그 내용을 </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;통보한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.3 품질감사 준비</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.3.1 감사자는 감사수행 전에 품질감사 체크리스트를 작성하여 감사준비를 한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.3.2 품질감사체크리스트 작성 시에는 다음과 같은 사항을 참고하여야 한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1) 피감사 팀에 관계되는 사내 표준, ISO 9001요건, 고객 요구사항 등.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(2) 과거 감사 시 지적사항.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(3) 피감사 팀의 품질목표</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(4) 피감사 팀의 주요 품질문제점 등.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.4 감사 실시</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";letter-spacing:0.3pt;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.4.1 품질감사는 품질시스템에 의거하여 객관적으로 실시하며 자신의 책임 하에</SPAN><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'> 수행된 업무는 감사할 수&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 없다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.4.2 감사자의 주관으로 감사시작 및 감사과정을 알리는 시작회의를 개최한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.4.3 시작회의 시에는 가능한 10분 이내가 되도록 한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;단, 품질감사 수행계획서에 의해 필요사항이 확정되면 시작회의를 생략 할 수 있다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.4.4 품질감사는 품질감사체크리스트에 따라 품질기록 등 객관적 사실에 의거 진행업무 및 결과가 적용&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 요건과의 일치여부를 확인한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";letter-spacing:0.2pt;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.4.5 품질감사는 피감사 팀의 업무현장에서 실제 활동내용을 대상으로 실시한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.4.6 품질감사는 다음과 같은 사항에 주안점을 두고 시행한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1) 업무방법 및 절차가 품질시스템 및 고객 요구사항과의 일치여부</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(2) 품질시스템이 합리적이고 효율적인가의 여부</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(3) 현재의 업무방법이 품질목표달성과 경제적 측면에서의 적절성 여부</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:150%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.4.7 품질감사수행 중 부적합 또는 문제점을 조사하며, 이에 관련된 품질시스템의 유무와 유효성을 평가&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 후 지적여부를 결정한다.</SPAN></P>

